## Where we Work

### From the Office

Our core team is located in Prague, Czech Republic and we're having a small office in Prague 5. We have capacity for five people on here, but mainly all people work remotely in Prague or any other city where they are living like Lima, Santiago de Chile, Zurich and Oslo.

### From the Coffee Shops

From time to time, we like to change of environment and we go to our favorite coffee places to get out there and enjoy a good cup of coffee.

### From Coworking spaces

Each of our team members represents Uppersky therefore we encourage our team to be part of co-working spaces where they can expand their network, feel the energy of a great community of startups and still help us to find new team members, partners & customers.



